            "text": "Importance of Time Management \n \nTime is one of the most valuable resources in our life . \nUnlike money or possessions, once time is gone, it can never be regained. \nGood time management helps u s finish our work on time, reduce stress, \nand create a balance between personal and professional life. \nPeople who manage their time well are more productive and successful. \nThey set clear goals, make priorities, and avoid wasting time on \nunimportant tasks."
